text: Start-Up (also known as Start-Up 2000) is a PC video game in which players must try to build a successful business start-up from venture capitalists to IPO's. Start-Up is published by Monte Cristo and distributed by Electronic Arts. == References == == External links == *Electronic Arts *Monte Cristo * Category:2000 video games Category:Electronic Arts games Category:North America-exclusive video games Category:Video games developed in France Category:Windows games Category:Windows-only games
